title: 268: Likes & Dislikes of Top Prospects
itunes:title: 268: Likes & Dislikes of Top Prospects
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks dissect the pros and cons of some of the top prospects when they put on the tape (2:23). DJ then breaks down what he saw when he recently watched Sam Darnold and Josh Allen train (28:13) before the guys each build the perfect team of prospects up the middle for both sides of the ball (34:01).
